Description:
    Scaffold an Controller an modules. Controller with the base Create,
    Update and Delete functions.

    Modules comes with the default json null object. so here add your Rails 
    model attributes here.

    Create Update and delete action url added to the 

Example:
    rails generate angular:scaffold product

    	Will create a controller called "products" it will contain initialize 
    	function. A model module will create under services/models directory,

    This will create:
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/controllers/products_controller.js.coffee
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/services/models/product.js.coffee

    This will update:
        app/assets/javascripts/angular/services/routes.js.coffee
